---
title: Easy Loaded Beef & Chorizo Jacket Potatoes with Cheddar Cheese & Garden Salad
description: Fancy some dapper potatoes, their jackets are razzled and dazzled with a cheesy topping of beef, cooked in a tomato sauce. if that’s not enough to tickle your fancy, then we’re sure the mild chorizo will really bring things to the next level.
